cdata.name: Scienceroot
cdata.desc:
Based on the Waves blockchain, Scienceroot is a decentralized platform that aims to improve the scientific and research community.By developing an ecosystem for the science community around the world, Scienceroot goal with the platform is to ease fund gathering, scientific community interaction and collaboration.

ST is a Waves-based token that will be used as a medium of exchange and as a reward for the authors and reviewers in the ecosystem.
